  "_comment": "Single source of truth for the landing-page ELEMENT CATALOG + composition (plans/PAGE_COMPOSER.md, Builder Reframe). Read by the Python publisher (domain/composition.py) AND imported by the Vue builder (composables/pageComposer.js). One vocabulary: the canonical key is the section `type` string (no aliases). Each element declares label + ui + kind + channel + heading_role + tokens; the composer uses governed_sections + offer_types (what the page sells) unioned with the packs enabled by goals (why its traffic comes \u2014 plans/LANDING_PAGE_GOAL_COMPOSITION.md).",
